# 18 BETA_ERRO ... Uncertainty of derived slope .................................
# 19 DISTANCE .... Derived (or assumed) distance ................................ pc
# 20 DIST_ERRO ... Uncertainty of derived distance .............................. pc
# 21 WAVE_TAU1 ... Wavelength where optical depth tau=1 ......................... µm
# 22 CHISQUARE ... Actual chi^2 value of the fit ................................
# 23 DEG_FREED ... Degrees of freedom of the fit ................................
